    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S represents a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the mid-mounted 3.4L flat-six engine delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from the optional Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) which provides excellent damping control and turn-in precision. Recent service includes a fresh water pump and thermostat, ensuring the cooling system maintains optimal operating temperatures during spirited drives. While showing minor signs of use consistent with its age, the mechanical integrity is robust, with the hydraulic steering rack providing the communicative feedback modern EPS systems lack. It sits on 19-inch Carrera S wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber with plenty of tread depth remaining.",
